transcript:
hey it's time that we talk about
boundaries just because you've known
someone for a while doesn't mean they
deserve to be around you anymore if
they're negative if they make you feel
worse about yourself if they make you
feel bad after leaving their presence if
they try to cut holes in all of your
successes if they're just bad for your
mental energy they need to go I don't
care how long you've known them I don't
care how important of a part they played
in your life if they are not good for
your mental energy they need to go just
because they're a part of your past
doesn't mean they deserve your future
